@startuml
autonumber
skinparam boxPadding 10
skinparam participantPadding 10
skinparam style strictuml

title File Manager with RTK Query & Spatie Permissions

actor "User" as User
box "Frontend (React + Redux Toolkit)" #E3F2FD
    participant "File Manager UI" as UI
    participant "RTK Query\n(fileManagerApi)" as RTK
end box

box "Backend (Laravel API)" #E8F5E9
    participant "Spatie\nMiddleware" as Auth
    participant "FileController" as API
    participant "Storage Facade" as Disk
end box

== 1. Fetch Files (Query) ==

User -> UI: Load / Navigate to Folder
activate UI

UI -> RTK: useGetFilesQuery('/docs')
activate RTK

RTK -> RTK: Check Cache ('Files', id: '/docs')

alt Cache Miss / Stale
    RTK -> Auth: GET /api/files?path=/docs
    activate Auth
    
    Auth -> Auth: user->can('read files')
    
    Auth -> API: Request Allowed
    activate API
    
    API -> Disk: Storage::files('/docs')
    activate Disk
    Disk --> API: List of files
    deactivate Disk
    
    API --> RTK: 200 OK [File Array]
    deactivate API
    deactivate Auth

    RTK -> RTK: Store in Cache\nProvide Tag: ['Files']
end

RTK --> UI: { data: [...], isLoading: false }
deactivate RTK
UI -> User: Render File List

== 2. Create Folder (Mutation) ==

User -> UI: Click "New Folder" -> Enter Name
UI -> RTK: useCreateFolderMutation({ path: '/', name: 'Images' })
activate RTK

RTK -> Auth: POST /api/files/folder
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: user->can('create folders')

Auth -> API: Request Allowed
activate API
API -> Disk: Storage::makeDirectory('/Images')
API --> RTK: 200 OK { message: "Created" }
deactivate API
deactivate Auth

RTK -> RTK: **Invalidate Tags: ['Files']**
note right of RTK
    RTK Query detects invalidation.
    Triggers auto-refetch of active queries.
end note

RTK -> Auth: GET /api/files?path=/ (Auto Refetch)
activate Auth
Auth -> API: ...
API --> RTK: Returns Updated List (with 'Images')
deactivate Auth
RTK --> UI: UI Updates Automatically
deactivate RTK

== 3. Upload File (Mutation) ==

User -> UI: Upload "photo.jpg"
UI -> RTK: useUploadFileMutation(FormData)
activate RTK

RTK -> Auth: POST /api/files/upload
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: user->can('upload files')

Auth -> API: Request Allowed
activate API
API -> Disk: Storage::putFileAs(...)
API --> RTK: 200 OK
deactivate API
deactivate Auth

RTK -> RTK: **Invalidate Tags: ['Files']**
RTK -> Auth: GET /api/files?path=/ (Auto Refetch)
activate Auth
Auth -> API: ...
API --> RTK: Returns Updated List
deactivate Auth
RTK --> UI: UI Updates Automatically
deactivate RTK

== 4. Rename Item (Mutation) ==

User -> UI: Rename "photo.jpg" to "pic.jpg"
UI -> RTK: useRenameMutation({ old: 'photo.jpg', new: 'pic.jpg' })
activate RTK

RTK -> Auth: POST /api/files/rename
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: user->can('rename files')

Auth -> API: Request Allowed
activate API
API -> Disk: Storage::move('photo.jpg', 'pic.jpg')
API --> RTK: 200 OK
deactivate API
deactivate Auth

RTK -> RTK: **Invalidate Tags: ['Files']**
RTK -> Auth: GET /api/files?path=/ (Auto Refetch)
activate Auth
Auth -> API: ...
API --> RTK: Returns Updated List
deactivate Auth
RTK --> UI: UI Updates Automatically
deactivate RTK

== 5. Download File (Lazy Query) ==

User -> UI: Click Download "report.pdf"
UI -> RTK: triggerDownload('/report.pdf')
activate RTK

RTK -> Auth: GET /api/files/download?path=/report.pdf
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: user->can('download files')

Auth -> API: Request Allowed
activate API
API -> Disk: Storage::download('/report.pdf')
activate Disk
Disk --> API: Stream Binary
deactivate Disk
API --> RTK: Blob / Binary Stream
deactivate API
deactivate Auth

RTK --> UI: Return Blob
deactivate RTK
UI -> User: Browser prompts "Save As"

== 6. Delete Item (Mutation) ==

User -> UI: Select "pic.jpg" -> Delete
UI -> RTK: useDeleteMutation({ path: 'pic.jpg' })
activate RTK

RTK -> Auth: DELETE /api/files/delete
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: user->can('delete files')

Auth -> API: Request Allowed
activate API
API -> Disk: Storage::delete('pic.jpg')
API --> RTK: 200 OK
deactivate API
deactivate Auth

RTK -> RTK: **Invalidate Tags: ['Files']**
RTK -> Auth: GET /api/files?path=/ (Auto Refetch)
activate Auth
Auth -> API: ...
API --> RTK: Returns Updated List (without 'pic.jpg')
deactivate Auth
RTK --> UI: UI Updates Automatically
deactivate RTK

@enduml